title: Vista Ultimate Sp1 32bit LITE with Office 2007-AiKo
description:
VISTA Ultimate Sp1 32bit LITE with Office 2007-AiKo

What you need to know about this version of MS Vista:

This is Fully Activated Vista Ultimate SP1 32bit, Slimmed down with vLite.

Minimum RAM requirement for installation is 256 MB, but recommended is 1GB+.
DEP is enabled for OS and processes, you can change this setting later.

On Disc you will find folders EXTRA which contains:

1. Software;
There you will find MS Office 2007 Enterprise ENG (no serial needed),
Unlocker (small utility which allows you to delete files in use) and
Prio (utility to permanently change process priority in Task Manager)

2. Stuff;
Some wallpapers (used from LastXP&#039;s Disc of windows XP)
Gadgets (some nice gadgets for sidebar)

For more details read INFO!
